Package: pdpr
Type: Package
Title: A package for downloading data from the Parliamentary Data Platform
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Oliver Hawkins
Maintainer: Oliver Hawkins <oli@olihawkins.com>
Description: This package provides functions for downloading data from the
    Parliamentary Data Platform. The core functions offer simple way to send
    SPARQL queries to the API endpoint and receive the results as a tibble 
    with data converted to the approriate R data type. In addition, convenience
    functions are provided for executing common queries.
License: BSD
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
	dplyr,
	httr,
	jsonlite,
	magrittr,
	purrr,
	readr,
	stringr,
	tibble
Suggests: testthat
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
